---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | Core & Balance Pilates" description="How Core & Balance Pilates collects, uses, and protects your information." noindex={true}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-20 prose">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>Last updated July 2026. Core & Balance Pilates ("we", "us") collects the information you provide when booking a
      class, joining our newsletter, or contacting the studio — including your name, email, phone number, and payment
      details processed securely by Stripe. We never sell your information.</p>
      <p>Information is used to manage bookings, send class confirmations and reminders, and respond to inquiries. We
      retain booking records as required for business and tax purposes.</p>
      <p>Payment information is processed directly by Stripe and never stored on our servers. See Stripe's own privacy
      policy for details on how they handle payment data.</p>
      <p>Questions about your data? Email us at hello@coreandbalancepilates.com.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
